    "description": "遗世界恋爱冒险『穿军靴的猫』<br><br>本游戏是通过阅读故事剧情，选择关键时刻弹出的选项，使得故事产生分歧的小说类冒险游戏。<br>玩家将成为和国的公主『玉』（※名字可以变更），目的是要在神秘废墟中的广阔的猫族世界中完成『试炼』。<br>和各个不同的攻略角色一起完成『试炼』，在此过程中，去孕育爱情，以幸福的结局为目标吧。<br><br>根据故事的发展，其中将会出现与正常选项不同的、存在时间限制的某种特殊的选项。<br>适当点击画面中最多显示的4个图标（或按下箭头键）来进行操作吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/e825129043e6d3845ea9702d1584e061.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/137de685a744c4dc39418733bf5aaef2.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br>这里是拥有“兽耳”和“尾巴”的「猫族」生活的世界。<br>猫族们将称为「人类」的神明作为「以试炼为代价，实现猫族们的愿望」的存在而崇拜着。<br>在废墟与自然融为一体的富饶国度「和国」。<br>身为公主的玉和她的堂兄小太郎的婚期将近，向「人类」报告婚讯的「婚礼之仪」的日子到来了。<br>仪式庄严举行着，就在本以为要顺利结束的那一瞬间，伴随着耀眼的光芒，一位青年出现了。<br>没有“兽耳”也没有“尾巴”的那副模样，正是猫族们所信仰的「人类」。<br>接着，「人类」的降临过去了数日。<br>因为遥远的海的另一边的「帝国」的来航，安稳和平的和国便迎来了试炼。<br>围绕着「人类」，和国与帝国怀着各自的思虑，将故事引向了动乱的前方。<br><br>作为一国公主、<br>　作为一只猫、<br>　　玉的选择是――――<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/5dc1df5dd1d61831e8f1583aea5238e7.webp?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>主角们生活的国家。<br>在这里，不知是谁所造的建筑物与自然非常和谐的融为一体。<br>以狩猎和简单工艺为主的『猫族』们各自过着自由自在的生活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/74f428cc0c3b057226fdef76c8e66271.webp?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>遥远西方的国家。<br>装饰豪华的建筑物所林立的中央部是其人民生活的中心，离开中央部的周围便是大片寂寥的荒野。<br>近年来沙漠化开始严重，水类资源逐渐稀缺。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/a5509f030233848a6885dc65a2880918.webp?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>名为『人类』的在『猫族』之间被传颂的传承性存在。<br>其外观除去没有兽耳和尾巴以外，和『猫族』没有任何区别。<br>相传，『人类』能为『猫族』带来试炼，完成试炼，便能实现愿望。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/71f6dc1cd6dff8315a43ea4835aeaa04.webp?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/33015d2d92e4d5ddf051e9433437e6e2.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/e29ea7615bf2ae7ebc577092c610c05b.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/5db839838ed4ece5000a9f94d44fac72.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/b99ccd0617613007213364de8d424eb4.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/476b7392a9358bda409fcc30d8cd3bac.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/102b035042710ec57cf622d4d45faf32.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/540a0ef1dfc561bd1b1f1a043dbf667e.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/70e166015332805f87a8715e593aab14.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/60dd45814074929716a93350e3c71292.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/7f066582288114e40686db7da352cce7.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/8c877354b159df3040837421027d4887.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/3aa8fd396c85bbe16430bcea222101f8.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/b4156763c2f8bdcf28c66d7f5c1a272b.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/2a4764ffc8337e50131364118f8d190a.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167430/extras/5a1d9d05c7a03645e418cc2e4217daf2.avif?t=1677225618\" width=616 height=336 /></span>",
